+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
|                      CLAIM TO EVIDENCE GRAPH                                   |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| CLAIM LANE                                                                     |
|   Claimed Level 3  --->  Achieved Level 3  --->  Next Blocked: Level 4        |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| AUTHORITY LANE                                                                 |
|   fidelity ladder doc  --->  maturity levels  --->  reducer contract          |
|   semantic graph        --->  capability bindings                             |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| EXECUTION LANE                                                                 |
|   resolver load  --->  evidence matrix  --->  achieved-level reduction        |
|   next-level compute blocked at fidelity.next_level.compute.v1                 |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| EVIDENCE LANE                                                                  |
|   contract-load receipt  --->  reducer receipt  --->  computed report         |
|   gate receipt           --->  run summary / release packet                   |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| BOUNDARY LANE                                                                  |
|   Level 4 proof missing: polish, accessibility, publish safety, equivalence   |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
